casebody.data:
Jabree HARRIS, Minor, BY Next Friend Ivory HARRIS, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Tammy FOX, Defendant,
and
Prime Healthcare Services-Garden City, LLC, d/b/a Garden City Hospital, Defendant-Appellee,
and
Bristol West Preferred Insurance Company, Defendant/Third-Party Plaintiff,
and
Metropolitan Group Property and Casualty Insurance Company, Third-Party Defendant. SC: 158884
COA: 340160 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 2, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the November 15, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
